Author: bonnginn
Text: I recently told my boyfriend. The first thing he did was go into our room and research. He then told me “I’m not going to bring it up, I won’t badger you about it at all” and he hasn’t. He goes as far as too play oblivious when certain issues arise. Maybe your bf is doing the same thing, giving you silent love and support so that you don’t feel the need to hide your habits and isolate.
